<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

  {{> navbar}}

  <div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">About DanceMove Academy</h1>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="mb-3">Our Story</h3>
            <p>DanceMove Academy was founded in 2015 with a simple mission: to make dance accessible to everyone. We believe that dance is not just an art form but a way to connect with others, build confidence, and express yourself.</p>
            
            <h3 class="mb-3 mt-4">Our Classes</h3>
            <p>We offer a variety of dance classes suitable for all ages and abilities:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Beginner to advanced levels</li>
              <li>Weekly courses and weekend workshops</li>
              <li>Various styles including hip-hop, contemporary, ballet, and more</li>
              <li>Private sessions and group classes</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mb-3 mt-4">Our Locations</h3>
            <p>We have multiple studios across Scotland:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Main Studio - Glasgow City Centre</li>
              <li>Southside Studio - Glasgow Southside</li>
              <li>Edinburgh Branch - Edinburgh Old Town</li>
              <li>Stirling Location - Stirling City Centre</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mb-3 mt-4">Contact Us</h3>
            <p>Have questions? Want to learn more about our classes?</p>
            <p>Email: info@dancemove.example.com<br>
               Phone: 0123 456 7890</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>